--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

A sample showing how to retrieve all topics of a given user.
Then topics are displayed with pagination and each post can be displayed - original url displayed in an iframe

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTRUCTIONS

- Install php5-curl
- Set up your access token in header.php

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

LINKS

- Scoop.it Developers Home : http://www.scoop.it/dev
- Scoop.it API Talk : http://groups.google.com/group/scoopit-api-talk
